    },
    {
      "id": "implication",
      "type": "markdown",
      "body": "## Implication For The Running Grid\n\nRows that improve morphology distance without improving medium/bad recall should be treated as proxy-insufficient. The next useful synthetic rules should preserve QRS for medium while adding P/T/ST unreliability, and reserve QRS-confounding pseudo-peaks/contact artifacts for bad."
    }
